  <p class="">Earlier this year DesignWays Conference integrated Footprint into the event organization and created outstanding results. In total it resulted in the following impact:</p><ul data-rte-list="default"><li><p class="">164 people have compensated their trip.</p></li><li><p class="">24198 KG CO2.</p></li><li><p class="">627 M2 forest have been saved.</p></li><li><p class="">360 M2 rainforest have been protected.</p></li></ul><h3>If you like to learn more about Footprint, connect with us.</h3><p class=""><a href="https://mango-chimes-mnpz.squarespace.com/events-stays">Learn more</a></p><p class=""><a href="mailto:sebastian@yourfootprint.co?subject=Footprint%20Workforce&amp;body=Dear%20Team%20at%20Footprint%2C%0A%0AI%20would%20like%20to%20know%20more%20about%20Footprint%20Workforce%20and%20how%20it%20can%20accelerate%20sustainability%20in%20my%20organization.%0A%0AThanks%20a%20lot!&amp;cc=daniel%40yourfootprint.co">Connect with us</a></p>]]></content:encoded><media:content type="image/png" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/0d44a1fb-52e9-48f4-bfe2-78bd410cf037/e9d1b-group1370.png?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="1859"><media:title type="plain">DesignWays Conference - Climate action with Footprint.</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>Akanksha Sharma | What role technology has in the sustainability world.</title><category>INNOVATION</category><dc:creator>Sebastian Gier</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 12 Sep 2022 16:26:54 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.footprint-intelligence.com/blog/akanksha-sharma-what-role-technology-has-in-the-sustainability-world</link><guid isPermaLink="false">646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7:64831b1c9bfe6002ab7095da:64831b3b9bfe6002ab7099c8</guid><description><![CDATA[In this episode of the Footprint Futures podcast, we talk with Akanksha 
