        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h3> 4. Offer more sustainable travel options:</h3><p class="">Offer more sustainable travel options: According to Bsales, in 95% of cases, travel accounts for more than 80% of your company’s footprint. First, an event can be held locally so travel through planes could be reduced to trains or cars. Another alternative is to offset the carbon emissions using Footprint Events &amp; Stays. Individuals can book their travel, whether it be for work or vacation, in a sustainable manner. Whether it be finding sustainable travel alternatives or finding sustainability projects to compensate as a way to offset emissions caused by your travel. Footprint Events &amp; Stays helps you organize everything from your plane, your stay and even your bus rides around the city while being sustainably conscious to reduce your footprint.</p>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
