        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h3>6. Use plastic-free cutlery and products:</h3><p class="">Plastic has an incredibly lengthy disintegration process, and it can take centuries to naturally decompose. Therefore, try using biodegradable disposable utensils that could reduce the use of plastic. To take it a step further, encourage attendees to bring their own reusable plates and cutlery to minimize any utensil waste.</p>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/4f5a465c-165c-47c5-84f9-e6dcad8babd7/2dd83-6.jpg" data-image-dimensions="2500x1696" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/4f5a465c-165c-47c5-84f9-e6dcad8babd7/2dd83-6.jpg?format=1000w" width="2500" height="1696" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/4f5a465c-165c-47c5-84f9-e6dcad8babd7/2dd83-6.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/4f5a465c-165c-47c5-84f9-e6dcad8babd7/2dd83-6.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/4f5a465c-165c-47c5-84f9-e6dcad8babd7/2dd83-6.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/4f5a465c-165c-47c5-84f9-e6dcad8babd7/2dd83-6.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/4f5a465c-165c-47c5-84f9-e6dcad8babd7/2dd83-6.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/4f5a465c-165c-47c5-84f9-e6dcad8babd7/2dd83-6.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/4f5a465c-165c-47c5-84f9-e6dcad8babd7/2dd83-6.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

                
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h3>7. Eliminate any paper products that are not necessary:</h3><p class="">With the rise of technology, the use of printed material is impractical. Especially given the interactive nature of apps and websites, switching to tech-based streams of communication and interaction is more productive and green. However, situations may arise that there are no alternatives to paper; in these cases, ensure there is a recycling station and that attendees are aware of it.</p>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/5d868616-a270-4561-a7af-190e47625e6f/131e0-7.jpg" data-image-dimensions="2500x1667" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/5d868616-a270-4561-a7af-190e47625e6f/131e0-7.jpg?format=1000w" width="2500" height="1667" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/5d868616-a270-4561-a7af-190e47625e6f/131e0-7.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/5d868616-a270-4561-a7af-190e47625e6f/131e0-7.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/5d868616-a270-4561-a7af-190e47625e6f/131e0-7.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/5d868616-a270-4561-a7af-190e47625e6f/131e0-7.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/5d868616-a270-4561-a7af-190e47625e6f/131e0-7.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/5d868616-a270-4561-a7af-190e47625e6f/131e0-7.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/5d868616-a270-4561-a7af-190e47625e6f/131e0-7.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

                
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h3>8. Locally source products for food, beverage or even event set up supplies:</h3><p class="">Choose suppliers that source locally and focus efforts on sustainability. This way not only is footprint decreased through less transportation and manufacturing, you are also sourcing more fresh and organic foods while helping the local economy.</p>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/eeeb41b4-c467-45f2-8f67-27736d45dbb4/a1814-8.jpg" data-image-dimensions="2500x1736" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/eeeb41b4-c467-45f2-8f67-27736d45dbb4/a1814-8.jpg?format=1000w" width="2500" height="1736" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/eeeb41b4-c467-45f2-8f67-27736d45dbb4/a1814-8.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/eeeb41b4-c467-45f2-8f67-27736d45dbb4/a1814-8.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/eeeb41b4-c467-45f2-8f67-27736d45dbb4/a1814-8.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/eeeb41b4-c467-45f2-8f67-27736d45dbb4/a1814-8.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/eeeb41b4-c467-45f2-8f67-27736d45dbb4/a1814-8.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/eeeb41b4-c467-45f2-8f67-27736d45dbb4/a1814-8.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/eeeb41b4-c467-45f2-8f67-27736d45dbb4/a1814-8.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

                
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h3>9. If possible, discuss opportunities in virtual or hybrid event options:</h3><p class="">To significantly decrease your footprint, as well as open opportunities to more flexible accommodation and less financial pressures, a good option is to see if your event can be transferred online into a virtual or hybrid type of event.</p>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/8cb1367c-ac43-4a91-930e-b38311adcf17/d00fd-chris-montgomery-smgtvepind4-unsplash.jpg" data-image-dimensions="2500x1875" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/8cb1367c-ac43-4a91-930e-b38311adcf17/d00fd-chris-montgomery-smgtvepind4-unsplash.jpg?format=1000w" width="2500" height="1875" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/8cb1367c-ac43-4a91-930e-b38311adcf17/d00fd-chris-montgomery-smgtvepind4-unsplash.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/8cb1367c-ac43-4a91-930e-b38311adcf17/d00fd-chris-montgomery-smgtvepind4-unsplash.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/8cb1367c-ac43-4a91-930e-b38311adcf17/d00fd-chris-montgomery-smgtvepind4-unsplash.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/8cb1367c-ac43-4a91-930e-b38311adcf17/d00fd-chris-montgomery-smgtvepind4-unsplash.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/8cb1367c-ac43-4a91-930e-b38311adcf17/d00fd-chris-montgomery-smgtvepind4-unsplash.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/8cb1367c-ac43-4a91-930e-b38311adcf17/d00fd-chris-montgomery-smgtvepind4-unsplash.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/8cb1367c-ac43-4a91-930e-b38311adcf17/d00fd-chris-montgomery-smgtvepind4-unsplash.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

                
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h3>10. Find sustainability topics that can be used for educational use:</h3><p class="">Communicate with attendees to learn about a sustainability topic with peak interest or that aligns with your companies’ mission and delegate a portion of your event to discuss it and find ways to alleviate environmental inequities within your community.</p>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
