  <p class="">Use the PropPickup: Store Pickup app to offer multiple shipping methods for customers to choose from. Customers are able to schedule their specific pickup date and time, whichever conveniently suits their needs.</p><p class=""><a href="https://apps.shopify.com/store-pickup-3">ProPickup</a></p><h2>2. Matrixify</h2>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
