  <p class="">Matrixify is a helpful tool that can manage your Shopify store data. Some key features Matrixify offers is backing up your whole shop, exporting your data to other platforms such as Google Marketplace, and copying your data to your other stores with only one zip or Excel file.</p><p class=""><a href="https://apps.shopify.com/excel-export-import?surface_detail=recommended-in-category&amp;surface_inter_position=1&amp;surface_intra_position=2&amp;surface_type=category">Matrixify</a></p><h2>3. ReStock: Back in Stock Alerts</h2>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
