  <p class="">Customers are easily able to subscribe to any out-of-stock items and they will receive emails as well as browser notifications that will notify the customer once that product is restocked. Some advanced features include: automatic/manual back in stock notification, multi-lingual widgets, and feature request and customize services.</p><p class=""><a href="https://apps.shopify.com/restock-alert?surface_detail=fulfillment-inventory-planning&amp;surface_inter_position=3&amp;surface_intra_position=3&amp;surface_type=category">ReStock</a></p><h2>4. AfterShip Order Tracking &amp; SMS</h2>














































  

    
  
    

      

      
