  <p class="">Using Gift Boxes will help create your own free gift setup which will help encourage and reward your customers. Spend ten dollars more in order to get free shipping, gift card, gift wrap, or free products.</p><p class=""><a href="https://apps.shopify.com/gift-box?surface_detail=conversion-promotions-gift-with-purchase&amp;surface_inter_position=6&amp;surface_intra_position=5&amp;surface_type=subcategory">Gift Box</a></p><p class=""><strong>From data management, to customer service and customizing CSS... these Shopify apps can help increase customer engagement, increase brand awareness, and are easily installable. This will not only benefit your business, but will save plenty of time too!</strong></p><h2>Hope you liked the article! ✌️</h2><p class="">If you liked the article we would appreciate it you share it with friends or family to raise awareness.</p>]]></content:encoded><media:content type="image/jpeg" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7/12658660-3e2f-43a8-afe8-99f82af24583/8bef8-unsplash_ejhjszkteeg.jpg?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="496"><media:title type="plain">10 Innovative Sustainable Apps on Shopify.</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>Henk Rogers | Accelerate clean energy.</title><category>INNOVATION</category><dc:creator>Sebastian Gier</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 16 Sep 2021 17:34:17 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.footprint-intelligence.com/blog/henk-rogers-accelerate-clean-energy</link><guid isPermaLink="false">646f9bfe5c10277d6cd432c7:64831b1c9bfe6002ab7095da:64831b309bfe6002ab70985a</guid><description><![CDATA[In this episode of the Footprint Futures podcast we talk with Henk Rogers, 
