        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Overall, humans are impacting the climate in drastic ways, and although the earth has been bailing us out of the worst effects, that won’t necessarily continue into the future. Going forward, each one of us needs to take action to reduce our individual climate impact, before it is too late. </p>




